# Target automation

- Folder is `target`; persisted keys/messages stay `retailer_*` / `RETAILER_*`.
- Session logic is split under `content/session/` — avoid re-monolithing.
- PDP selectors: `lib/selectors.ts`; checkout: `lib/checkout/selectors.ts` — see `extension/domains/target/docs/TARGET_AUTOMATION.md`.
- Backend ATC must run in page context via `public/injected/cart-probe.js`, not content script.
- One automation job at a time (`tryAcquireRetailerJob`); do not bypass mutex.
- Hard refresh resume uses Target tab `sessionStorage` (`auto-resume.ts`).

See `extension/domains/target/AGENTS.md`.
